   DEBUG: 2026-03-29 12:25:30,289:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 1.1 Purpose
   DEBUG: 2026-03-29 12:25:30,292:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: A Test Automation Framework for the 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-29 12:25:30,295:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: KFIC Loan Origination System (LOS)
   DEBUG: 2026-03-29 12:25:30,325:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: . Automates browser-based
   DEBUG: 2026-03-29 12:25:30,330:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: operations — login, form filling, approvals, and closures — that were previously performed manually.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-29 12:25:30,331:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 1.2 Objectives
   DEBUG: 2026-03-29 12:25:30,333:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-03-29 12:25:30,335:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Eliminate repetitive manual testing.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-29 12:25:30,338:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-03-29 12:25:30,340:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Reduce human errors.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-29 12:25:30,342:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-03-29 12:25:30,344:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Enable fast, accurate, and repeatable test execution.
